<Link id="l00398" /><CodeLine lineNumber="398" lineLink="/docs/api/classes/llvm/logicalview/lvtypeparam/#a9d91a965b3081fd5950e15b1da04cf13"><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordType">void</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/logicalview/lvtypeparam/#a9d91a965b3081fd5950e15b1da04cf13">LVTypeParam::encodeTemplateArgument</a>(std::string &amp;<a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/logicalview/#af64c789b30b79a5f18889270bccef27ea49ee3087348e8d44e1feda1917443987">Name</a>)</span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword"> const </span><span class="doxyHighlight">&#123;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00399" /><CodeLine lineNumber="399"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// The incoming type is a template parameter; we have 3 kinds of parameters:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00400" /><CodeLine lineNumber="400"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// - type parameter: resolve the instance (type);</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00401" /><CodeLine lineNumber="401"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// - value parameter: resolve the constant value</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00402" /><CodeLine lineNumber="402"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// - template parameter: resolve the name of the template.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00403" /><CodeLine lineNumber="403"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// If the parameter type is a template instance (STL sample), we need to</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00404" /><CodeLine lineNumber="404"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// expand the type (template template case). For the following variable</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00405" /><CodeLine lineNumber="405"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// declarations:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00406" /><CodeLine lineNumber="406"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   std::type&lt;float&gt; a&#95;float;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00407" /><CodeLine lineNumber="407"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   std::type&lt;int&gt; a&#95;int;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00408" /><CodeLine lineNumber="408"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// We must generate names like:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00409" /><CodeLine lineNumber="409"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   &quot;std::type&lt;float,std::less&lt;float&gt;,std::allocator&lt;float&gt;,false&gt;&quot;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00410" /><CodeLine lineNumber="410"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   &quot;std::type&lt;int,std::less&lt;int&gt;,std::allocator&lt;int&gt;,false&gt;&quot;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00411" /><CodeLine lineNumber="411"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// Instead of the incomplete names:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00412" /><CodeLine lineNumber="412"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   &quot;type&lt;float,less,allocator,false&gt;&quot;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00413" /><CodeLine lineNumber="413"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   &quot;type&lt;int,less,allocator,false&gt;&quot;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00414" /><CodeLine lineNumber="414"></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00415" /><CodeLine lineNumber="415"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">if</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> (getIsTemplateTypeParam()) &#123;</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00418" /><CodeLine lineNumber="418"></CodeLine>
